Revision history for Dist-Zilla-Rinci-Wrap

0.09    2015-03-06 (PERLANCAR)

        - [Bugfix] Fix variable names.


0.08    2015-02-26 (PERLANCAR)

	- Generate code to set $SPEC{foo} to the new metadata returned by
	  wrapper, not the old one (e.g. with logs entry, result_naked etc
	  normalized).


0.07    2015-02-25 (PERLANCAR)

	- Put in '## this line put by Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Rinci::Wrap'
	  markers in the source code.


0.06     2015-02-22 (PERLANCAR)

         - Observe #NO_RINCI_WRAP directive.

         - [ux] Instead of complaining about missing prereq in dist.ini, add
           dynamically with register_prereqs().


0.05     2014-03-15 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes. Fix missing dependency to Dist::Zilla [CT].


0.04     2014-03-08 (SHARYANTO)

         - Some more fixes.

         - Observe x.dist.zilla.plugin.rinci.wrap.wrap_args attribute in
           function metadata to let functions customize their wrapping.


0.03     2014-03-08 (SHARYANTO)

         - Check modules required by wrapper code in dist.ini's Prereqs.


0.02     2014-03-08 (SHARYANTO)

         - Minor fixes and tidy output.

         - Add marker comments on debug.


0.01     2014-03-07 (SHARYANTO)

         - First release.
